These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: french, russian
2 different pets are kept: lizard, guinea-pig
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, zinnia
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski
1. the french is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Nationality       | russian       | french |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | lizard  |
| Flower       | zinnia    | balloon-flower    |
| Transport   | jet-ski       | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: german, indonesian
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, time-travel
City: hannover, liverpool
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Nationality      | indonesian     | german |
| Hobby           | filmmaking | skydiving      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | action      |
| City         | hannover | liverpool     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, parkour
There 2 different types of food: apple, avocado
The people have 2 different jobs:  scientist, paramedic
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: iris, bellflower
1. the paramedic is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who growsbellflower##1
3. the person eating apple is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Sport      | biathlon | parkour  |
| Food          | apple    | avocado   |
| Job   | paramedic  | scientist   |
| Flower     | bellflower     | iris |

