There 2 different types of food: lemon, papaya
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, skateboard
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, cycling
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| City      | prague       | edinburgh |
| Food          | papaya         | lemon    |
| Transport           | skateboard | snowmobile    |
| Sport   | climbing           | cycling   |

