.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, security-guard
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, ivory
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, puzzles
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, pall-mall
1. the coach is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
2. the coach is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | security-guard | coach     |
| Color   | fuchsia          | ivory |
| Hobby           | writing          | puzzles    |
| Cigar     | pall-mall            | baccarat       |

 